Ever wonder which gaming console truly changed everything? I just spent $450 on a 50 year old Magnavox Odyssey to find out. From Nintendo's biggest comeback to Xbox's most devastating failure, these 5 consoles didn't just succeed or fail – they completely reshaped gaming forever. But which one deserves the crown as the MOST important console of all time?
